        </div>
      <div class="page-heading">
        <h2 class="page-heading-text">About Us</h2>
       </div>
       <div class="page-text">
        <p>CrimeTracker is a community crime policing system. Created by Apiwe Macingwane(3831144) , Honor Student from the University of the Western Cape.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="page-heading">
        <h2 class="page-heading-text">Why Crime Tracker ?</h2>
       </div>
       <div class="page-text">
        <p>The more we come together to fight crime the tougher it gets for criminals. Become an ACTIVE citizen. Which will allow us to  build a safer community. <br> It is designed to allow open sharing of crime activities for crime prevention and planning. Information is public and provided freely to the community.   </p>
      </div>
    
       <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">        
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
                <div class="white-box ">
                  <div>
                    <h3>Details</h3>
                    <form action="/write-query" method="post">
                        <div class="form-input"><input type="text" name="fullname" placeholder="Enter your name"></div>
                        <div class="form-input"><input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address"></div>
                        <div class="form-input"><textarea name="description" cols="40" rows="10" placeholder="Write your query..."></textarea></div> 
                        <div><button class="form-button btn btn-primary" type="submit">Submit</button></div>
                    </form>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="map"></div>
                    <script>
                        var map = tt.map({
                            key: "BoLC9waGtIqMa7OF8GeW1E7cdODwiohH",
                            container: "map",
                            center: [18.629438,-33.894272], 
                            zoom:14,
                            "cluster": true,
                            "clusterRadius": 70
                            });
                        folium.Circle(
                        radius=5000,
                        color='crimson',
                        fill=False,).add_to(map)
                    </script>
                    </div>
    
        </div>
